Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.22,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My name is Asai Yuki, 23 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:12.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm in my 3rd year working at a small to medium sized event planning company, I'm a promising employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:17.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I had dinner for the first time with my colleague Riko, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:24.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why am I building a plastic model???
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Congratulations for getting the CEO award.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy to see a new events department member has improved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:32.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is also doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:43.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, another round of lemon sour please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:44.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about you, Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:46.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:48.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Could it be that I'm getting promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, about Department 3 getting dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't joke about such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:58.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:04.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lately Department 3 is looking like a real team,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,don't you think that it's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can't we do anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I won't be making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's a bit harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Aren't you close with the members of Department 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If Department 3 is dissolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,what will happen to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They will be on different departments,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,or maybe some of them will leave the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They made this decision based on their performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will go talk to the higher ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you, but I can't give you my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If give a proper explanation, surely the higher ups will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:43.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the end, they don't know anything about what's going on in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You sure are confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm the company's next ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The actual survey results shows that there is a high demand for actually experiencing it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As I have just explained, the nature of events department is undergoing a major shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:05.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was well put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,May I have a moment of everyone's time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:16.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If Department 3 is dissolved, it will have a repercussion for Department 1 and 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that is the best solution for everyone involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Above all, it is imperative that we establish a new digital department.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If anything, the whole events department needs to be expanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the time to be aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that the Mirai Expo event was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me, thank Manten-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,From now on, I will not keep things to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We don't have any major events in the works, so let's take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:47.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi is leaving the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is he leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's going to the biggest company in the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's so good at his job after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't do anything about it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do your best, Komukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so motivated, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about whether I should confess or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? \N-To Chiemi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's the only one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that you already confessed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:37.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Confessing your love without any confidence is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, could it be that you're in the same boat, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to confess, Riko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Finally to Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's finally that time, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have any confidence nor there's a possibility to succeed, so it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You said that you wanted to get cuter for Oishi-san's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen Nakano-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that and confessing are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you assuming that I never confessed my love before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it even a confession if you know there's a chance to succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're being weird, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it's a bother to receive a love confession from someone that you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you confessed your love to someone before, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a bit unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:10.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's all too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:21.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's clear as day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Be confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to help you out, so do your best until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern me, but I don't want it to end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't do something like that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:13.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So, the proposal that you presented out of the blue during the board meeting didn't come to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I did something similar before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You should have stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I won't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You understand that passion alone is not enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a chance for Department 3 to survive if they won a big competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:44.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, can I find such a perfect competition right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is our line of work exclusive to the private sector?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:55.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's the pride and joy of our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's working hard for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:24.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:31.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:32.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I may have found a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:34.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, just wait a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, did Oishi-san said something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just how prideful are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We have to get a result this time, by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This won't affect my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're getting transferred next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:20.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To the digital department?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To HR.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's someone who is on paternity leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's an important department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me in HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got the CEO award the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone here has won the CEO award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Want to grab something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:07.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It feels like I lost all of my strength in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:15.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You couldn't stop Oishi-san from leaving after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for making you help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san is leaving the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:23.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I don't. When did you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you at the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We were talking about the dissolvement of Department 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Department 3 is getting dissolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait wait wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way that you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No I don't. Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard it from Saruwatari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about you supporting me to confess my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:51.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you like Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about confessing before he leaves the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My head can't keep up with all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So what's going to happen to us working at Department 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As you said, I can't give up on Department 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's my colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It must be hard on you to be told that out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:19.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did my passion count for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that you told me that I'm a mass-production type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was annoyed back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're also a mass-production type person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't pick a fight at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not picking a fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pay for all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:52.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so I want you to follow me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's my colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He works hard for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But a lot of things happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:08.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I felt a lot better after building plastic models here with you and Chiemi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:33.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why am I building a plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sober now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You were focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't remember? I'm Yassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Chiemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you going to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I promised her after she paid for all the {\i1}sake{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was also an office worker back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He quit his job and then started this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with the rough spots as we work our way through the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A 400 smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to smooth out the left over gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm motivated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If so, then I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the first time this year that he's this serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This time, you use glue in the beginning to remove the seam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Apply to both sides of the part and press firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You should use more glue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you have confirmed that the glue is all dried up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's time to remove the excess glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's time to paint them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But before that, let's wash them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:12.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wash?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:16.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The surface of the parts are covered with hand grease and release agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up, is to paint the undercoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a process called surfacer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:35.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is used to fill in fine scratches, eliminate unevenness in color and improve the adhesion of the paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:44.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you find a flaw, smooth it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to paint it again afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:03.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're free to use any color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tone it any way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:08.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can airbrush it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Use ink for the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:32.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:37.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do this part too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:38.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:44.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Finally, do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:50.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:51.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:06.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I can still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Get rid of the shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:38.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is not a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:10.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,High Grade RGM-79 'GM'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Although it has been more than 20 years since its release,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the proportions are still convincing even when assembled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As a mass-production type mobile suit, you won't get bored no matter how much you build them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's still being supported by the fans to this day, truly a famous kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,GM...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,GM was developed based on operational data from the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Based on the design of the Gundam, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,by eliminating the expensive mechanism and lowering the cost
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:37.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it became a mass-produced mobile suit that boasted overwhelming production power and was used by the Earth Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The specs are on par with those of the Principality of Zeon's mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks similar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a Gundam, but a mass-production mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I found this GM the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:59.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Other than Zaku, there are another mass-produced mobile suit in the Gundam universe called GM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the next ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My goal is to become the next ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Work using your own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I getting promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time to be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rest assured, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asai. You're getting transferred next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}HR?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:36.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not close to that mass-production type employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got the CEO award the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:42.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when you become a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job finishing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This GM...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I believed from the bottom of my heart that I was a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But today for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like I properly saw my own face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The body of a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But the head is a GM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a GM of the company,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that can be easily replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If I'm a Zaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,then you're a GM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm currently a GM,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that being a mass-production type person is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:21.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can freely customize your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I love Department 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to get dissolved, so I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:10.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that if Department 3 managed to get this, there's a chance that it will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a COOL JAPAN event competition in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's still time to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is all that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:23.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm still in shock about Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:29.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:31.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I still count on your support for me confessing to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you that was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:34.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have a surprisingly egregious personality, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:37.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:38.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,